HEADWORD: encode
<hw>en*code"</hw> <pr>(⟦ecr⟧n*k⟦omac⟧d")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To
convert (a text, data) into a series of secret symbols by means of a
<er>code</er>{5}; to encrypt.</def> ⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> encrypt, code, encipher, cipher, cypher, inscribe,
write in code.</syn>⟦br⟧
